- cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing): The paper deals with processing of audio signals, which can be considered as a type of signal processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a probabilistic model and uses Bayesian inference, which are common techniques in machine learning. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with processing of audio signals, which can be considered as a type of multimedia data. 
- cs.SDQ (Sound and Music Computing): The paper deals with processing of music signals, which falls under the domain of sound and music computing.
